# Curator-promoted session artifacts live here.
# This file exists so the directory is tracked in git even when empty.
#
# To promote a session, copy the entire .claude/session-artifacts/<id>/
# directory into this folder under a descriptive name, e.g.:
#
#   ark-mono-connector-routing/
#   multi-agent-subagent-anchoring/
#
# The regression test at tests/regression/ark-mono-connector-routing.md
# is the first candidate for exemplar promotion.
